column2: SELECT type2_table.plate, type2_table.mjd, type2_table.fiber, type2_table.z, type2_table.survey_id, type2_table.velocity_disp, type2_table.trust_stellar_fit, type2_table.oiii_hbeta, type2_table.velocity_disp_new, type2_table.velocity_disp_new_err, photo.petroMag_u, photo.petroMag_g, photo.petroMag_r, photo.petroMag_i, photo.petroMag_z, photo.petroMagErr_u, photo.petroMagErr_g, photo.petroMagErr_r, photo.petroMagErr_i, photo.petroMagErr_z, tmass.J_M_K2#FE, tmass.H_M_K2#FE, tmass.K_M_K2#FE, tmass.J_MSIG_K2#FE, tmass.H_MSIG_K2#FE, tmass.K_MSIG_K2#FE, FROM MyDB.initial_type2_table as type2_table JOIN specobj as spec ON ( (spec.plate = type2_table.plate) AND (spec.mjd = type2_table.mjd) AND (spec.fiberid = type2_table.fiber) ) JOIN photoobj as photo ON (spec.specobjid = photo.specobjid) JOIN TwoMassXSC as tmass ON (tmass.objid = photo.objid)
